name: The Fighter
description:
Entered via: Objkt4objkt rift #20210909
Power level: Creeper
Size: 6.5 feet/2 meters tall
Aspect: Madness
Secondary Aspects: Unique, OBJKT4OBJKT

Bloodshed is the only language she knows, her fists dripping in the juices of her opponents. 

She loves nothing more than smashing the head of her opponent with her fist, but won't hesitate to utilize anything and everything in order to defeat whatever opposes her. The Fighter is a deadly creature that commands fear, and is best fought using ranged weapons from cover.
